### Articles API Examples

@backend_origin = https://your-backend-host.tld
@base = {{backend_origin}}/api

GET {{base}}/articles?page=1&limit=5
Accept: application/json

### Search
GET {{base}}/articles?q=Sample&page=1&limit=5
Accept: application/json

### Meta Counts
GET {{base}}/articles/meta
Accept: application/json

### Get One (replace ID)
GET {{base}}/articles/{{ARTICLE_ID}}
Accept: application/json

### Create (requires Bearer token)
POST {{base}}/articles
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "title": "CLI Created Article",
  "summary": "Created from .http collection",
  "content": "<p>Body</p>",
  "category": "Breaking",
  "tags": ["cli","test"],
  "language": "en",
  "status": "draft"
}

### Archive
PATCH {{base}}/articles/{{ARTICLE_ID}}/archive
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Restore
PATCH {{base}}/articles/{{ARTICLE_ID}}/restore
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Soft Delete
DELETE {{base}}/articles/{{ARTICLE_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
